Package no.ntnu.idata.shiporganizer.shiporganizerservice.model

Class User

java.lang.Object
no.ntnu.idata.shiporganizer.shiporganizerservice.model.User
@Entity public class User extends Object
Represents a user of the ship organizer service. Implements UserDetails for use with Spring Security authentication.
